data.description:
Can you say EQUITY??? This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with bonus room has so many options to be a wonderful investment OR your home. Home inspection with estimates available. This home needs a few cosmetic updates (estimates available), and is priced for these improvements-and you will STILL will have equity. Situated in a small neighborhood in Hope Mills with a spacious backyard. ROOF 2021. HVAC 2017/2019.  Your search is over, Welcome Home!
